text: Valery Dvoryaninov (born 6 November 1947) is a Soviet equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tashkent
